  <h2>Cultural Landscape</h2>
  <p>The Ith-Region has a rich history. Historic town centres, traditional crafts and an active community life shape the cultural life in Salzhemmendorf and Coppenbrügge.</p>
  <h3>Historical Highlights</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Coppenbrügge Castle</strong> – Medieval castle with museum</li>
    <li><strong>Historic Salzhemmendorf</strong> – Half-timbered architecture and salt history</li>
    <li><strong>Traditional Customs</strong> – Marksmen's festivals, harvest festivals and fairs</li>
    <li><strong>Local Crafts</strong> – Regional artisans and workshops</li>
  </ul>
